    "5": {
      "title": "section_5",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Orcish_Plate_ArmorCC\"><span id=\"Orcish_Plate_Armor\"></span>Orcish Plate Armor<sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Orcish_Plate\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Orcish Plate\">CC</a></sup></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Orcish&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Orcish Plate ArmorCC\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Orcish Plate is a heavy armor variant added by the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Orcish_Plate\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Orcish Plate\">Alternative Armors - Orcish Plate</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">Creation</a>.\n</p><p>Every piece has a higher value, and a slightly higher armor rating than their regular counterpart, except for the helmet, which retains the armor rating of the regular version (possibly due to an oversight). It also lacks a shield variant. Its total armor rating is a bit lower than <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Ebony_Armor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Ebony Armor\">ebony armor</a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Orcish_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/43/SR-item-Orcish_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg/200px-SR-item-Orcish_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/43/SR-item-Orcish_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg/300px-SR-item-Orcish_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/4/43/SR-item-Orcish_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg/400px-SR-item-Orcish_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Orcish_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A female <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Imperial\" title=\"Skyrim:Imperial\">Imperial</a> wearing orcish plate armor</div></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Armor Rating\"><img alt=\"Armor Rating\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/22px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/33px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/44px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"3\" class=\"unsortable\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Delta\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Ratio\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Orichalcum_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Orichalcum Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6b/SR-icon-ingot-Orichalcum_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Orichalcum_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6b/SR-icon-ingot-Orichalcum_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Orichalcum_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/6/6b/SR-icon-ingot-Orichalcum_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Orichalcum_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Orichalcum_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Orichalcum Ingot\">Orichalcum</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Iron Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/01/SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/01/SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/0/01/SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Iron_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Iron Ingot\">Iron</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/48px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Leather_Strips\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Leather Strips\">Strips</a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Armor.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Orcish Plate Armor.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/16/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Armor.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Armor.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/16/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Armor.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Armor.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/1/16/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Armor.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Armor.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Orcish_Plate_Armor\"></span>Orcish Plate Armor<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">801</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>35</td>\n<td>1100</td>\n<td>41\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">4</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black; color:red\">29.7\n</td>\n<td>904\n</td>\n<td style=\"color:red\">6.60\n</td>\n<td>5.61\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Boots.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Orcish Plate Boots.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/18/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Boots.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Boots.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/1/18/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Boots.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Boots.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/1/18/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Boots.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Boots.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Orcish_Plate_Boots\"></span>Orcish Plate Boots<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">800</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>225</td>\n<td>16\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">3</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black; color:red\">2.8\n</td>\n<td>77\n</td>\n<td style=\"color:red\">1.67\n</td>\n<td>1.52\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Gauntlets.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Orcish Plate Gauntlets.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/81/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Gauntlets.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Gauntlets.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/81/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Gauntlets.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Gauntlets.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/8/81/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Gauntlets.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Gauntlets.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Orcish_Plate_Gauntlets\"></span>Orcish Plate Gauntlets<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">802</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>225</td>\n<td>16\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">2</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black; color:red\">3.8\n</td>\n<td>122\n</td>\n<td style=\"color:red\">2.19\n</td>\n<td>2.18\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Plate_Helmet.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Orcish Plate Helmet.png\" src=\"