    "6": {
      "title": "section_6",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Orcish_Scaled_ArmorCC\"><span id=\"Orcish_Scaled_Armor\"></span>Orcish Scaled Armor<sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Orcish_Scaled\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Orcish Scaled\">CC</a></sup></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Orcish&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Orcish Scaled ArmorCC\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Orcish Scaled is a <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Light_Armor\" title=\"Skyrim:Light Armor\">light armor</a> variant added by the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Orcish_Scaled\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Orcish Scaled\">Alternative Armors - Orcish Scaled</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">Creation</a>.\n</p><p>In terms of armor rating, it's only slightly worse than <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dragonscale_Armor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Dragonscale Armor\">dragonscale armor</a>, but it weighs considerably more, just 1 point shy of the heavy <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dwarven_Mail\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Dwarven Mail\">dwarven mail</a><sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Dwarven_Mail\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Dwarven Mail\">CC</a></sup> light armor. It also lacks a shield.\n</p>\n<ul><li>&#32;At a Blacksmith Forge, Orcish Scaled items do not appear under the Orcish category, but rather under Misc.<ul><li>  The <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Special_Edition_Patch\" title=\"Skyrim:Special Edition Patch\">Official Skyrim Special Edition Patch</a>, version 1.6.1130.0, fixes this bug. </li></ul></li></ul>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Orcish_Scaled_Armor_Male.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d3/SR-item-Orcish_Scaled_Armor_Male.jpg/200px-SR-item-Orcish_Scaled_Armor_Male.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d3/SR-item-Orcish_Scaled_Armor_Male.jpg/300px-SR-item-Orcish_Scaled_Armor_Male.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d3/SR-item-Orcish_Scaled_Armor_Male.jpg/400px-SR-item-Orcish_Scaled_Armor_Male.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Orcish_Scaled_Armor_Male.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A male <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Nord\" title=\"Skyrim:Nord\">Nord</a> wearing orcish scaled armor</div></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png