ps.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/48px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Leather_Strips\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Leather Strips\">Strips</a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Armor.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Orcish Scaled Armor.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/88/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Armor.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Armor.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/88/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Armor.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Armor.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/8/88/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Armor.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Armor.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Orcish_Scaled_Armor\"></span>Orcish Scaled Armor<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">801</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>14</td>\n<td>500</td>\n<td>36\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">4</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black; color:red\">4.7\n</td>\n<td>304\n</td>\n<td style=\"color:red\">1.51\n</td>\n<td>2.55\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Boots.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Orcish Scaled Boots.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/23/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Boots.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Boots.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/23/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Boots.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Boots.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/23/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Boots.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Boots.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Orcish_Scaled_Boots\"></span>Orcish Scaled Boots<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">800</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>150</td>\n<td>13\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">3</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>2\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">-0.3\n</td>\n<td>2\n</td>\n<td>0.93\n</td>\n<td>1.01\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Gauntlets.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Orcish Scaled Gauntlets.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d3/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Gauntlets.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Gauntlets.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d3/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Gauntlets.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Gauntlets.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d3/SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Gauntlets.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Orcish_Scaled_Gauntlets.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Orcish_Scaled_Gauntlets\"></span>Orcish Scaled Gauntlets<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for mor